      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu wiꞥſch betdsis De- winna Dehſe / un tee ſaudis/ dsamo-Uppuri uppureht / raugt / kas pee wiꞥſceem atraddahs/ pa- tad atnahze Samuels. Un Sauls likke us Benjamika Pakalnu/ iſgahje tam pretti winnu ſweh- Bet tee Wilisterti bij Mikmaſa tiht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Samuels: ko eſſi tu darrıjs? Un Sauls fazztja: Tapehz ka es redſeju/ ka tee Lan- dis pakak mannim iſkaifijahs/ un tu noſiktā Laika ne nahzi/un tee Wilisterti Mikmaſā kohpā bij fapulzejſchees:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazziju eß : Nu no- nahks tee Wilisterti pee man uhs Gilgalu/ un es ne efmu ta KUN- GA Waigu peeluhdſis/ tad es eedrohſchinajohs/ un uppureju Dedsamo-Uppuri.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Samuels us Saulu: Tu eſſi appłam darrijs/ tu ne eſſi ta KUNGA tawa Deewa Bauſti turrejs/ ko wiꞥſch tev irr pawehlejs/ jo nu buhtu tas KUNGS tawn Walſtibu pahr Israēlu apſtiprinajs muh- schigi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet nu tawa Walſtiba ne pastahwehs/ tas KUNGS irr fevim weenu Wihru meklejs pehz tawas Girds/ un tas KUNGS irr tam pawehlejs par Waldita- ju buht pahr faweem Landim/ta- pehz/ ka tu ne eſſi turrejs/ fo tas KUNGS tew bij pawehlejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad zehlehs Samuels/ un gabje no Gilgala uhs Gibeju Benjamitzā/ un Sauls lihdsina- ja tohs ſaudis/ kas pee wiꞥſca at- raddahs/ pee ſefchſints Wihreem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Sauls un Jonatans\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un no to Wilisternu Leh- gera iſgahje trihs Pulkı Samai- tatajo/ weens Bulks greesehs us to Zeltu prett Owru/us to Sem- mi Sualu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un weens Pulks greesehs us to Zeltu prett Bet-Ohronu/ un weens Pulks greesehs us to Koh- beschas Zeltu/ kas us to Eeletju Zeboim prett Tukſneft ſteepjahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ne tahds Kallejs tappa atrasts ceſsch wiſtas Israēta Semnes. Jo tee Wilisterti bi fazzıſchi : Laid tee Eebreeri ne kahdu Sohbinu neds Schlehpu padarra.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tadeht bij wiſamı Israē tam pee teem Wilistereem ja-eet ka kursch sawu Leminefi / Kap su/ jeb sawu Zirwi/ jeb sawu Js kaptu likka tezzinaht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee Afimini vee teem Je kapteem/ un Kapleem/ un Trisa reem/ un Zirwjeem bija atzirsti/u tee Dsennuti bija atkat jatezzina\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un paſchā Ranschana Deena / ne tappe Sohbins ne Schlehps atrasts wiſfu Lausch Rohkā/ kas pee Saula un pee J natanabija/ bet pee Saula/un p Jonatana winna Dehla tap atraste.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un to Wilisternu Spei zehlehs us to pahretjamu We garx Mikmaſu.\n"
    }
  ],
